%%{init: {"sequence": {"messageMargin": 64, "noteMargin": 24, "boxMargin": 18, "wrap": true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Voter
    participant App as Voting App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database

    User->>App: Enter name, DOB, postcode, town of birth
    App->>App: Build lookup payload
    App->>App: Encrypt payload
    App->>Server: POST /api/voter/lookup-for-auth

    Server->>Server: Decrypt + validate fields
    Server->>DB: Find voter candidates by SDI
    DB-->>Server: Matching voter records

    alt Single voter match
        Server-->>App: 200 OK with voterId
        App-->>User: Voter found
        Note over App,Server: Continues to voter-auth-dataflow-only
    else Multiple matches (collision)
        Server-->>App: 400 requiresDisambiguation + candidate IDs
        App-->>User: Multiple matches found, continue to fingerprint scan
        Note over App,Server: Continues to voter-auth-dataflow-only collision path
    else Already voted
        Server-->>App: 400 already voted
        App-->>User: Stop and request official assistance
    else No match
        Server-->>App: 400 voter not found
        App-->>User: Check details and try again
    end
